original_title: Power Rangers Time Force: The End of Time
overview: Jen, Katie, Lucas and Trip receive a panicked call from Alex. Frax, he warns, is building Doomtron, a super-robot that will destroy the city. If the teens don't return to the future (3000) now, the won't survive. Wes, however, must stay in his own era - 2001 - so the teens stay and help him fight.
title: Power Rangers Time Force: The End of Time
